2. Drain the engine coolant. (Refer to 01-12 ENGINE COOLANT REPLACEMENT, Draining.) 
3. Remove the dashboard. (Refer to 09-17 DASHBOARD REMOVAL/INSTALLATION.) 
4. Remove the seal plate.  

